495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not expecting that, but he can do anything,\\\" she shared at the time.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Anything is possible in Christ.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9797623266077723, \"rank\": 0.020655696597788164, \"text\": \"Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anything\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So yeah, I am just amazed, baffled, and in shock.\\\"\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shock\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone, a devout Christian who attended Union Catholic High School in Scotch Plains, New Jersey, often references Scripture and gives thanks to God in interviews and acrosssocial media.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9988891086402979, \"rank\": 0.000993276378477804, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999413057612, \"rank\": 5.7412772357187513e-08, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http:/