ited_States\"}, {\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999715678318, \"rank\": 2.465998848598237e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone's former principal\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"withCNAin\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"her pride\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"her former student\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the track star\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"that instrument\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her spontaneity at the end of her victory when she praised God and gave all the glory to God translates to me that she is God's instrument for being a power for good worldwide,\\\" Hart continued.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her spontaneity\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"her victory\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"all the glory\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"God's instrument\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"a power\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"Hart\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are all called to become all God calls us to be, and be good people, and Sydney models that, and affirms that with her messages about faith.\\\"\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999995060180792, \"rank\": 4.769757392322181e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all God\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"good people\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"her messages\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Further sharing her faith life, the three-time Olympic medalist released her memoir in January of this year, titled \\\"Far Beyond Gold: Running from Fear to Faith.\\\"\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her faith life\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-time Olympic medalist\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"her memoir\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Far Beyond Gold\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"Fear\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"Faith\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout thebook, McLaughlin-Levrone details her past experiences of struggling with anxiety and perfection while also highlighting the ways she glorifies God both on and off the track.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thebook\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"her past experiences\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a Christian, I now existed to glorify God (1 Corinthians 6:19-20; Matthew 5:16).\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9988891086402979, \"rank\": 0.000993276378477804, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"(1 Corinthians\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the beginning of 2021, I was learning all the way my life wasn't about me.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"all the way\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was about showing the world God's power, wisdom, kindness, love, and forgiveness,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"God's power\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"wisdom\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were a bunch of different ways to do that.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bunch\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"different ways\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Off the track, I could do that by serving others, putting their needs before mine, and being excited when God did a remarkable work in their lives (Philippians 2:3-4).\\\"\", \"from\": 2123, \